title: Old Town Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Beer/Wine, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Casual, independently owned cafe that uses mostly organic, local ingredients. A majority of the menu (breakfast and lunch) is vegetarian, a few vegan options, some gluten free options. There are 5 meat dishes in total (on the lunch menu).
